---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = '/penzana-del-merel';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Family — La Penzana del Merel"
  description="The Merelli family: Alessandro, Tarcisio, Efrem, and Laura. Three generations of Bergamo passion for pizza, the oven, and genuine hospitality."
  lang="en"
  currentPath={`${base}/en/family/`}
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-block:clamp(3rem,8vw,5rem);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Family</span>
      <h1>The Merelli Family</h1>
      <p>Three generations united by one passion: an oven, a pizza, and a place in Valle Seriana where people keep coming back.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">
      <div class="grid-2" style="gap:3rem; align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <h2>Alessandro Merelli</h2>
          <span class="card-label" style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The founder · 1936</span>
          <p>Alessandro acquired the building in 1936, laying the first stone of what would become a landmark for Orezzo and the Valle Seriana. His intuition — recognising the potential of the place — is where everything began.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Tarcisio Merelli</h2>
          <span class="card-label" style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Master pizza maker · 1959–present</span>
          <p>Tarcisio opens the inn on 31 December 1959. His passion for bread ovens leads him to build them himself — and in 1989 he reaches the <strong>final of the Naples Centenary of the Margherita pizza</strong>. A rare achievement for a Bergamo craftsman, still a point of pride for the family.</p>
          <p>In the 1990s he transforms the inn into a pizzeria, together with his family, inventing the name still used today.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Efrem Merelli</h2>
          <span class="card-label" style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Second generation</span>
          <p>Tarcisio's son, Efrem supports his father in the transformation into a pizzeria. He carries on the family tradition with careful attention to ingredient quality and customer care.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Laura Merla</h2>
          <span class="card-label" style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The heart of the family</span>
          <p>Efrem's wife, Laura has been an integral part of running the place since the pizzeria's early days. Her presence contributes to the genuine warmth that customers remember.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <figure class="reveal" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <img src={`${base}/img/team_2020.png`} alt="Family and staff group photo with Santa hats" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" />
        <figcaption style="font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:0.5rem; font-style:italic; text-align:center;">The family and staff — always together</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <blockquote class="pullquote" style="margin-top:3rem;">
        The Merelli family never stopped believing that the place mattered as much as the pizza. And perhaps that is why people keep coming back.
      </blockquote>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem; display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href={`${base}/en/history/`} class="btn btn-green">Full history</a>
        <a href={`${base}/en/contact/`} class="btn btn-outline" style="color:var(--green-deep); border-color:var(--stone-xlight);">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</BaseLayout>
